* Various patterns or phenomena that appear in the heavens. Phenomena occurring in the heavens (universe) or celestial bodies. ⇒ '''{{ill|Astronomical phenomena|ja|天文現象}}'''
* The act or skill of divining fortunes by observing various phenomena in the sky. → {{ill|Astronomical divination|ja|天文道}}, {{ill|Temmon Hakase|ja|天文博士}}
* A [[Japan|Japanese]] {{ill|era name|ja|元号}}. → {{ill|Tenmon (era)|ja|天文 (元号)}}

== Related terms ==
* {{ill|Observatory|ja|天文台}} (a facility for observing the state of the heavens)
* {{ill|Tenmon Keito|ja|天文瓊統}}
* {{ill|Tenmongata|ja|天文方}}
* {{ill|Amateur astronomy|ja|天文家}}
* {{ill|Astronomy|ja|天文学}}, {{ill|Astronomer|ja|天文学者}}
* {{Prefix}}
* {{Intitle}}

